Subject: MacOS Endpoint Protector client vulnerability
Description: I am trialling Endpoint Protector on two Macbooks. These MacBooks are running Microsoft Defender. Defender has picked up that the Endpoint Protector software on these two MacBooks has a vulnerability CVE-2012-2994. I am running Endpoint Protector Client 3.0.3.1009.
